ProtoTheorem:
. "Let $R$ be a ring with $a, b \in R$. Then \begin{enumerate}
   \item \it $a0 = 0a = 0$; \item \it $a(-b) = (-a)b = -ab$; 
   \item \it $(-a)(-b) =ab$. \end{enumerate}"
